{"tid":264662,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"（多圖整合）厹借93K IG偽稱支持創作暗溝女窮追不捨","createTime":"2017-05-31T04:14:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-02T00:16:25.000Z","uid":72613,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"88e11658d47de877e2c4a3399b7e33b60c8355fe","tid":264662,"uid":72613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T04:14:31.000Z","msg":"一個名為 HKSHARE 的分享圖片平台（簡稱S）借幫助插畫人士之名，開啟WHATSAPP群組並招募喜歡插畫人士並訛稱供給一個地方讓大家交流。<br />\n<br />\n罪名一：死纏爛打<br />\n(S) 透過 Whatsapp 對 兩位受害人（A) 及（B) 不斷纏繞，即使兩位女方清楚表明立場但男方亦死心不惜，封鎖後仍利用其他途徑表示心意。<br />\n(A)<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/113719_a44df9a08195194d4be2537171a6754c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F113719_a44df9a08195194d4be2537171a6754c.jpg&h=ec873c4e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/113719_bf950e703e94df0dc6bcdde1d8a8d8ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F113719_bf950e703e94df0dc6bcdde1d8a8d8ac.jpg&h=96d79c55&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/113721_6adcca946ad0e238d913a12561d8c352.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F113721_6adcca946ad0e238d913a12561d8c352.jpg&h=6490d948&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(B)<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/114937_877a435f50ea654e7fc8eb168d58b860.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F114937_877a435f50ea654e7fc8eb168d58b860.jpg&h=351a0a80&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/114939_05a50795710c3a27bd7a90f8cce754e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F114939_05a50795710c3a27bd7a90f8cce754e0.jpg&h=e361c867&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/114940_5cc313f49d82deb55c53c53cec8769f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F114940_5cc313f49d82deb55c53c53cec8769f1.jpg&h=77ed6c13&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/114941_dee1b09e528aa6749ba5320e91d1bc8e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F114941_dee1b09e528aa6749ba5320e91d1bc8e.jpg&h=49af46fb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/114942_dee1b09e528aa6749ba5320e91d1bc8e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F114942_dee1b09e528aa6749ba5320e91d1bc8e.jpg&h=aae6f159&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為事件緣故，期間（B)離開了插畫群組，<br />\n而（S)表示若（B)不進回該群組則解散整個WhatsApp群並不再幫忙所有人分享圖片。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/120051_2d4b6ae1694c1ecad4e37cbc45d5cc60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F120051_2d4b6ae1694c1ecad4e37cbc45d5cc60.jpg&h=9dc2d0c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/115103_de61e2acfb0d45b86f80f92030af24a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F115103_de61e2acfb0d45b86f80f92030af24a1.jpg&h=90025690&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其後，男方認為事件不能這樣結束，開啟了一個假的account偽稱自己為Sherry，打算以假身份偽稱幫助分享插畫，假裝女生但說自已是男校，其後被識穿以粗話完結<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/115855_595f18eb02e3c6a189ba43569ee2e0fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F115855_595f18eb02e3c6a189ba43569ee2e0fb.jpg&h=45a0724f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/115856_3c4bfa1818925c405260e12ee24e1f5e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F115856_3c4bfa1818925c405260e12ee24e1f5e.jpg&h=41beb513&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/115856_910f3e1b09b6e4358ef0164ad9f181f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F115856_910f3e1b09b6e4358ef0164ad9f181f7.jpg&h=e8a52dd8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/115900_910f3e1b09b6e4358ef0164ad9f181f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F115900_910f3e1b09b6e4358ef0164ad9f181f7.jpg&h=fa182fb3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/115903_bb3616b321b4cd6876fa594e3b995c1c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F115903_bb3616b321b4cd6876fa594e3b995c1c.jpg&h=963b2f21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n罪名二：自大狂妄<br />\nHKSHARE表示不用一年時間就能建立宏舉（93K追蹤者），並踐踏插畫人士的追蹤人數低的都是廢物，但卻借以幫忙投稿之名支持創作，名不符實<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/120301_3ae94cfd8c935129805b03e2654c4389.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F120301_3ae94cfd8c935129805b03e2654c4389.jpg&h=b2e0d1bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/120458_5e9171baec3bbb71f377fd6915b99fad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F120458_5e9171baec3bbb71f377fd6915b99fad.jpg&h=122fa7e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n罪名三：死不悔改<br />\n近日亦於IG story中提供電話號碼，提出可以幫忙投稿或跟他聊天，繼續以投稿之明暗裡溝女。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/120302_76c1f2255e1fe2419736aef25075f146.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F120302_76c1f2255e1fe2419736aef25075f146.jpg&h=ce4e41a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n罪名四：偷竊圖片<br />\n（S)平台內九成都是偷取其他圖片當作自己分享。<br />\n昨天，(S)將其中一名插畫家的私人生活照加文字作為自己的圖片發佈，當時人表示從來沒有允許而且（S）是從她的臉書偷取作己用。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/120754_60b5cc77d3d315e4dcd90cc0d5765019.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F120754_60b5cc77d3d315e4dcd90cc0d5765019.jpg&h=c3aef71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以幫忙檢舉(S)的偷圖平台，<br />\n以及提防此狗公。"},{"pid":"6d3f43c4695acbc8f4bf2a68043128065f334615","tid":264662,"uid":76117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T04:18:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"946691c66d699b0047d79fcd0c1c7515a411390d","tid":264662,"uid":72613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T04:23:36.000Z","msg":"原post : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/255057?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/255057?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n基於有巴打話死圖同建議轉台再開<br />\n所以重新開一個"},{"pid":"2720e079436307fe15a18459c6acfb16934ab7d8","tid":264662,"uid":72613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T04:36:03.000Z","msg":"[quote]上述亦有提及過（S)開了一個名為插畫交流的群組，當中發生經過由插畫顯示給大家了解。<br />\n插畫：文妮 <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/122536_bf324483c5bea40103e53bb605202a82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F122536_bf324483c5bea40103e53bb605202a82.jpg&h=b9cbcaf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n啊昌 即是 （S)<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/122626_0b98f3608471e7a0ac2faa682bffea81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F122626_0b98f3608471e7a0ac2faa682bffea81.jpg&h=91d38296&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後，（S) 將插畫人士們加入到他所開的「插畫交流群」。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/122652_7887ff3386b9a943b77803a66f5b6abd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F122652_7887ff3386b9a943b77803a66f5b6abd.jpg&h=aac17abe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/122653_7887ff3386b9a943b77803a66f5b6abd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F122653_7887ff3386b9a943b77803a66f5b6abd.jpg&h=42d6ea1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家有共同興趣，聊天投契之下<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/122753_a63ee72faa0f28afbc7f1c47fd2a9894.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F122753_a63ee72faa0f28afbc7f1c47fd2a9894.jpg&h=d1892b17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/122754_a63ee72faa0f28afbc7f1c47fd2a9894.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F122754_a63ee72faa0f28afbc7f1c47fd2a9894.jpg&h=247cd2b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/122758_5f48f993a1d3ca3740b5c4d83458a639.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F122758_5f48f993a1d3ca3740b5c4d83458a639.jpg&h=e927fcac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/122922_707a7a99b9baa5c19539f1c55e0ac4f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F122922_707a7a99b9baa5c19539f1c55e0ac4f0.jpg&h=1e7c3517&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/122800_69a8d8bd1efef1f8171d14eb44e0adcf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F122800_69a8d8bd1efef1f8171d14eb44e0adcf.jpg&h=c5e0fe05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/123415_3c126f8a4d182ac8cfa44b4fd98d9543.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F123415_3c126f8a4d182ac8cfa44b4fd98d9543.jpg&h=f25131ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/123418_3c126f8a4d182ac8cfa44b4fd98d9543.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F123418_3c126f8a4d182ac8cfa44b4fd98d9543.jpg&h=21827341&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/123419_043df71a224c5d2f50b318b18326715b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F123419_043df71a224c5d2f50b318b18326715b.jpg&h=69535f20&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c302fd504fb43bc770ba7eea1b5ddb984c26bcd","tid":264662,"uid":72613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T04:42:30.000Z","msg":"簡稱（B)<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/123909_d29186c5d0fdd04c12f4d87dc51cf361.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F123909_d29186c5d0fdd04c12f4d87dc51cf361.jpg&h=9194bca6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n解散後<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/123944_a0041927ab453add8458ab55ff081d5f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F123944_a0041927ab453add8458ab55ff081d5f.jpg&h=47b43d91&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/123946_3155ac1359b41710bd76adf0937d3600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F123946_3155ac1359b41710bd76adf0937d3600.jpg&h=ea36263c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基於搵錯路去錯相反方向既巴士站，所以決定去搭地鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  企地鐵全程都好靜同無講過野<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/124040_192fe346721256a6421364c857a79b86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F124040_192fe346721256a6421364c857a79b86.jpg&h=9a58d15d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後（S)打開話題<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/124057_1df7f1f55a623ca198106a99c913d348.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F124057_1df7f1f55a623ca198106a99c913d348.jpg&h=44ce6a4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（B) 表示我只係想快啲落車 ...<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/124114_cb92cae604c6fcfdcf5ed1fac5bd8019.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F124114_cb92cae604c6fcfdcf5ed1fac5bd8019.jpg&h=d3ac5c9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n插畫：文妮<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>然後一切<span style=\"color: red;\">厹事件</span>和<span style=\"color: red;\">Sherry事件</span><br />\n就是在<span style=\"color: red;\">這次聚會後</span>發生的。</strong></span>"},{"pid":"fe98b0344d908d87bbccaaa6c357c992892a5106","tid":264662,"uid":72613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T07:41:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e4bd01b74d4f642d49436eb5461b3d69015e041","tid":264662,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T05:43:35.000Z","msg":"留名跟進<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43dfa0599dd645457ba703839117e55afc7cb399","tid":264662,"uid":110790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T00:16:25.000Z","msg":"Hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}